The <a href="http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=25349" rel="nofollow">Next To Me Songfacts</a> reports that this song finds Sandé celebrating the strong, loyal men in her life. She told The Boombox: &quot;I'm lucky that I have had very strong men in my life and who have always been very loyal to me, from my dad, my manager, to my fiancé.&quot;

 Having won the coveted Critics' Choice Gong at the Brit Awards, hugely talented singer-songwriter <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/Emeli+Sand%C3%A9" class="bbcode_artist">Emeli Sand&eacute;</a> scored a No.2 smash with her third single 'Next To Me' in February 2012. The 24 year old, who swapped a medical career for music, then raced to No.1 in the UK with her debut album '<a title="Emeli Sand&eacute; - Our Version of Events" href="http://www.last.fm/music/Emeli+Sand%C3%A9/Our+Version+of+Events" class="bbcode_album">Our Version of Events</a>' to round off an incredible month.

